snippet: The Nationals prodded their fans to show up for home games and keep Philadelphia’s followers out. The plan failed.
abstract: Philadelphia Phillies followers come out in force for weekend series against Washington Nationals in Washington, despite Nationals Take Back the Park campaign prodding Nationals fans to show up for home games and keep Phillies fans out.
lead_paragraph: The Nationals prodded their fans to show up for home games and keep Philadelphia’s followers out. The plan failed.

headline.seo: Nationals Fail to Halt Invasion of Phillies Fans
headline.main: Uninvited, Phillies Fans Still March In
headline.print_headline: Uninvited, Phillies Fans Still March In
